item.title: About Me
item.description: Nauman Khan Biography Nauman Khan Introduction My name is Muhammad Nauman Alam Khan and I was born and brought up in Paksitan, where I spent the first 16 years of my life. It was during my formative years that I was initially introduced to field hockey, a sport that I would go on to dedicate most of the next decade of my life to. Hockey I first played the sport casually at school before trying out for the school team, of which I became the captain of in my second year on the team.
